channel.title: Anyone got "starting files"?
channel.description:
Hi. I wanna learn a bit programmin (well, pretty much everything you humanly possible could know about it :P). so I wondered why there isnt a "starter pack" for newbis. that includes the non edited code of mopar(w/e).
I dont want do download "h4ckpkmegauberscape 2004 v2.0259 build 1½" wich has been edited by around 40 persons and 35 didnt know what they did. :eek:
so if anyone got them. please send em! after a few(million) tutorials, Ill think i can start working on my own.
(much more fun editing a current source then making a new one, right?) but i dont want a spoiled source including a comment every second line saying: \\not made by blaho \\made by blahi \\made by blaha
